Requirements:

  * Python 2.6 or newer. (not tested on older versions)
  * pyparsing-1.5.5 module
    <http://pyparsing.wikispaces.com>
  * lxml module  
    <http://codespeak.net/lxml>
  * wikitools 1.1.1 module
    <http://code.google.com/p/python-wikitools>  
  * py2exe 0.6.9 module for creating executable files for MS Windows
    <https://sourceforge.net/projects/py2exe/>

  * YouTube Video Downloader  
    For Windows: Windows standalone version of youtube-dl.py 
    For Unix: youtube-dl.py 
   <http://www.himili.com/blog/downloads/youtube-video-downloader/>  
    